</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_52" id="25v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_52_r1l21"><expan>VVeiſſemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_52_r1l22"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan> / Vns hat fürgelegt Hans von Castell der Schuͤcʒ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_52_r1l23">vvie daʒ Jn der Chuncʒ Lehner <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> mitburger von <expan>vverltlıch<ex>er</ex></expan> ſache </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_52_r1l28">vvegen auf geiſtlich geriht gen <expan>Bamb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> geladen 
<add><ab facs="#facs_52_line_1576492676515_8914">vnd cʒu pan braht </ab></add> hab / 
<del rend="strikethrough">vnd vvir </del> das vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_52_r1l29">
<del rend="strikethrough">doch </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_52_line_1576492724213_8967">von <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> ~ <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> vn
<del rend="strikethrough">d</del></ab><ab facs="#facs_52_line_1576492726444_8972">glimplich dunkt </ab><ab facs="#facs_52_line_1576492728177_8977"><expan>vvan<ex>n</ex></expan> wir </ab></add> <expan>demſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ~ <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> mitburger des rehten von <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_52_r1l32"><expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒuhelffen nẏe <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſagt</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>mitburg<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_52_r1l34"><expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> daran weiſen wöllet / daʒ Er <expan>dieſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> klag auf </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_52_r1l35"><expan>geiſtliche<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>rehte<ex>n</ex></expan> abtü / Als etc / das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc Vnd het dann </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_52_r1l36">derſelb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>mitburg<ex>er</ex></expan> / cʒu dem <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> ıcht <expan>cʒeſprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_52_r1l37"><expan>dar<ex>ümb</ex></expan> <expan>vvölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir Jm oder <expan>ſeine<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>ſch<ex>einboten</ex></expan> etc ut in <expan>for<ex>ma</ex></expan> / <expan>Antvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_52" id="25v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Weissemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, uns hat fürgelegt Hans von Castell, der
                        Schuͤcz, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>, wie daz in der Chuncz Lehner,
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> mitburger, von
                                <expan>werltlich<ex>er</ex></expan> sache wegen auf geistlich geriht
                        gen <expan>Bamb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> geladen <add>und czu pan braht</add>
                        hab, das uns <add>von <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> un glimplich dunkt,
                                <expan>wan<ex>n</ex></expan> wir</add>
<expan>demselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> mitburger des rehten von
                            <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> czuhelffen nye
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>sagt</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir
                                <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>mitburg<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> daran weisen wöllet, daz er
                                <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> klag auf
                                <expan>geistliche<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>rehte<ex>n</ex></expan> abtü, als etc. Das
                            <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. Und het dann derselb
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>mitburg<ex>er</ex></expan> czu dem
                            <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> icht <expan>czesprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan>,
                                <expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
<expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir im oder <expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>sch<ex>einboten</ex></expan> etc. ut in
                        <expan>for<ex>ma</ex></expan>. <expan>Antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> etc.</ab>
</div>
